msgstr "O quadrado x^2 de x."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "sqrt(x)"
msgstr "sqrt(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid "The square root of x."
msgstr "A raiz quadrada de x."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid "sign(x)"
msgstr "sign(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sign of x. Returns 1 if x is positive, 0 if x is zero, or &minus;1 if x "
"is negative."
msgstr ""
"O sinal de x. Devolve 1, se o 'x' for positivo, 0 se 'x' for zero e &minus;1 "
"se for negativo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "H(x)"
msgstr "H(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Heaviside Step Function. Returns 1 if x is positive, 0.5 if x is zero, "
"or 0 if x is negative."
msgstr ""
"A Função de Heaviside. Devolve 1 se o 'x' for positivo, 0,5 se o 'x' for "
"igual a zero ou 0 se o 'x' for negativo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
